spec_data.Name: rubygem-selenium-webdriver
spec_data.Description:
WebDriver is a tool for writing automated tests of websites. It aims to mimic
the behavior of a real user, and as such interacts with the HTML of the
application.

spec_data.Summary: The next generation developer focused tool for automated testing of webapps
